  m_text: "Starting setup -\n Draw 7 cards\n\nPlace 1 Basic Pokemon as your active.
    You can put up to 5 Basic Pokemon on your Bench \n\nEach turn starts by drawing
    1 card, then you can play cards, and usually ends with an attack.  \n\nYou can
    attach only 1 Energy card per turn from your hand. \n\nOnce you attack, your
    turn is over (unless a card effect says otherwise).\n\nPok\xE9mon can evolve
    only once per turn They cannot evolve the same turn they are played"
