      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "1.) Flip of a coin determines what player decides to go first \n\n\n2.)
    each player shuffles 20-30 cards in their deck \n\n3.) players can place up to
    5 basic cards in their bench or active spot\n\n4.) fter player puts their card
    in the active spot put top 3 of cards as points \n\n5.) If your Active Pok\xE9mon
    is Confused, check now to see if its attack doesn\u2019t happen.\n\n6.) Apply
    any effects that happen before damage, then place damage counters, and then do
    all other effects.\n\n7.) There are 3 main types: Pokemon, Trainer cards, Energy
    cards"
